<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- hl qd dẖbḥt mn ạ̉jly .. wdẖqt ạ̉hwạl ạlṣlyb
 whl ạ̉ḥnyt rạ̉sk .. ltḥml ʿạry ạlmdẖyb

[V2]
 2- ḍrbt ʿny hnạk .. sḥqt sḥqạaⁿ bạlṣlyb
 wfwqh sạlt dmạk .. lạ̉jl dẖnby ạlmʿyb

[V3]
 3- hl kl hdẖh ạlậlạm .. hl kl hdẖạ ạlạktỷạb
 hl kl dẖlk ạlhwạn .. ʿny ạ̉nạ hdẖạ ạlʿdẖạb

[V4]
 4- ʿny ạ̉nạ nʿm ʿny .. ḥbh ly sạm ʿjyb
 ysẖdw bh trnmy ạ̹dẖ .. qd fdạny bạlṣlyb</lyrics>
<title>hl qd dẖbḥt mn ạ̉jly</title>
